Type: Package
Package: geoidep
Title: Download Geographic Data on Various Topics Provided and Managed by
    the Spatial Data Infrastructure of Peru
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: 
    person("antony", "barja", , "geografo.pe@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5921-2858"))
Description: Provides R users with easy access to official cartographic
    data from Peru across a range of topics, including society, transport,
    environment, agriculture, climate, and more.  It also includes data
    from regional government entities and technical-scientific
    institutions, all managed by Peru's Spatial Data Infrastructure.  For
    more information, please visit:
    <https://www.geoidep.gob.pe/catalogos-de-metadatos>.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
URL: https://geografo.pe/geoidep/
BugReports: https://github.com/ambarja/geoidep/issues
